<LP>
   DEFIANCE Inc. (Defiance, Ohio) -- Thomas H. Roulston Sr.,
president and chief executive officer, was named chairman of
this supplier of technology and products to manufacturers in
the transportation industry. Mr. Roulston succeeds Allen J.
Portnoy, who remains a director.
   ---
</LP>
<TEXT>
   Corrections &amp; Amplifications
                                                                                                       

   THOMAS H. ROULSTON SR. was named chairman of Defiance Inc.
In yesterday's edition, it was incorrectly stated that Mr.
Roulston was Defiance's president and chief executive
officer.
   (WSJ July 3, 1990)
